# Force Git to treat these as binary and never touch line endings in them,
# regardless of autocrlf settings. Without this, Git's binary-detection
# heuristic can occasionally misfire on some binary formats and silently
# corrupt them via LF/CRLF conversion.
*.pdf binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
